  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<p>Overall supervision of assigned projects, to ensure timely completion of projects, within the approved budgets set by the Project Manager and the management.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>Plan and prepare all project micro and/or master program with indication of Critical Path to complete assigned projects in a timely manner.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>To liaise with all subcontractors, consultants and owners on project matters and to resolve all technical discrepancies and site issues.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>To supervise and ensure that acceptable workmanship and quality of projects are obtained to the management and consultants’ approval. \t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>To attend, prepare and report on project progress, milestones and targets during meetings. \t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>To organise and to chair regular site meetings with subcontractors, NSCs and suppliers. \t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p>Any other adhoc projects and duties as assigned by management.\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n<p><br></p>",
